  "text": "Manganese is also released in acid soils. Eight triticale genotypes which differed in Al tolerance were tested in nutrient solution for manganese tolerance [CITATION_1] . A wide range of Mn tolerance was found but it did not correlate across genotypes with Al tolerance. Selection for acid soil tolerance should therefore consider both metals.",
